definitions.definition: Used to express that something is exceedingly bad , awful , or terrible .
examples: - The one day I actually practice my violin, the teacher cancels the lesson. - Aw, rubbish ! Though at least this means you have time to play football.

definitions.definition: Used to express that what was recently said is nonsense or untrue ; balderdash !, nonsense!
examples: Rubbish ! I did nothing of the sort!

main_definition: Used to express that something is exceedingly bad , awful , or terrible .
secondary_definitions: Used to express that what was recently said is nonsense or untrue ; balderdash !, nonsense!
